<section class="relative bg-primary-950 text-white py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tighter reveal">
      제조사의 첫 유통 경험을 <span class="text-accent-500">설계합니다</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-8 text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed reveal delay-200">
      와디즈 런칭부터 라이브커머스, 공동구매, 폐쇄몰 입점까지. <br class="hidden md:block" />
      제조사에게 꼭 필요한 실무형 유통 경험을 선사합니다.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6 reveal delay-400">
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white font-black py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl text-lg transition-all shadow-xl shadow-accent-500/20 active:scale-95">
        무료 유통 상담 받기
      </a>
      <a href="/services/utongstart" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-bold py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl text-lg backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-all active:scale-95">
        서비스 자세히 보기
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img src="/images/hero/hero-main.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 hidden md:block" />
    <img src="/images/hero/hero-mobile.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 md:hidden" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950 via-primary-950/80 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-500 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-primary-500 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
  </div>
</section>
